  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/349250/extras/8b9a2d4977efb5daad522801b6e7dea9.poster.avif?t=1681233034\" width=560 height=282 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/349250/extras/8b9a2d4977efb5daad522801b6e7dea9.webm?t=1681233034\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/349250/extras/8b9a2d4977efb5daad522801b6e7dea9.mp4?t=1681233034\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Blast robots in cyberspace!</h2>Boki wants to be a hero, but isn't quite there yet. Her uncle Savant built a virtual reality combat program so Boki can practice, and become the superhero she's always wanted to be! <br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/349250/extras/cc59d5cd897e778046d3e01e2f780724.poster.avif?t=1681233034\" width=560 height=316 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/349250/extras/cc59d5cd897e778046d3e01e2f780724.webm?t=1681233034\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/349250/extras/cc59d5cd897e778046d3e01e2f780724.mp4?t=1681233034\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Tons of cool weapons!</h2>Boki can copy powers from enemies, and then combine up to <strong>3 at a time</strong>. Each of the 175 combinations have been hand-crafted to be as cool as possible! <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/349250/extras/1e6a4a609f8469ba60a97c02ccf0529d.poster.avif?t=1681233034\" width=560 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/349250/extras/1e6a4a609f8469ba60a97c02ccf0529d.webm?t=1681233034\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/349250/extras/1e6a4a609f8469ba60a97c02ccf0529d.mp4?t=1681233034\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A massive level editor!</h2>Make your own custom missions - and absolutely <i>everything</i> is customizable. Mix and match enemies with different weapons, and even make your own multi-phase boss battles! Share your levels with friends, or upload them to Steam Workshop.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/349250/extras/0014c21e2c2fe6963c3565c8a5ceb526.poster.avif?t=1681233034\" width=560 height=314 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/349250/extras/0014c21e2c2fe6963c3565c8a5ceb526.webm?t=1681233034\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/349250/extras/0014c21e2c2fe6963c3565c8a5ceb526.mp4?t=1681233034\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Other stuff:</h2>• <strong>13 worlds</strong> in story mode, with over 20 bosses total<br>• <strong>Hard Mode</strong> as a continuation of the main story, with new enemies and cutscenes<br>• <strong>Endless Mode</strong> with 37 environments, and bosses with randomized attacks<br>• <strong>Play as Savant</strong>, with completely different abilities and 100 new weapons<br>• <strong>A free demo</strong> with 5 worlds, the standard path in Endless, and a limited version of the editor",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/349250/extras/8b9a2d4977efb5daad522801b6e7dea9.poster.avif?t=1681233034\" width=560 height=282 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/349250/extras/8b9a2d4977efb5daad522801b6e7dea9.webm?t=1681233034\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/349250/extras/8b9a2d4977efb5daad522801b6e7dea9.mp4?t=1681233034\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Blast robots in cyberspace!</h2>Boki wants to be a hero, but isn't quite there yet. Her uncle Savant built a virtual reality combat program so Boki can practice, and become the superhero she's always wanted to be! <br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/349250/extras/cc59d5cd897e778046d3e01e2f780724.poster.avif?t=1681233034\" width=560 height=316 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/349250/extras/cc59d5cd897e778046d3e01e2f780724.webm?t=1681233034\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/349250/extras/cc59d5cd897e778046d3e01e2f780724.mp4?t=1681233034\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Tons of cool weapons!</h2>Boki can copy powers from enemies, and then combine up to <strong>3 at a time</strong>. Each of the 175 combinations have been hand-crafted to be as cool as possible! <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/349250/extras/1e6a4a609f8469ba60a97c02ccf0529d.poster.avif?t=1681233034\" width=560 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/349250/extras/1e6a4a609f8469ba60a97c02ccf0529d.webm?t=1681233034\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/349250/extras/1e6a4a609f8469ba60a97c02ccf0529d.mp4?t=1681233034\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A massive level editor!</h2>Make your own custom missions - and absolutely <i>everything</i> is customizable. Mix and match enemies with different weapons, and even make your own multi-phase boss battles! Share your levels with friends, or upload them to Steam Workshop.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/349250/extras/0014c21e2c2fe6963c3565c8a5ceb526.poster.avif?t=1681233034\" width=560 height=314 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/349250/extras/0014c21e2c2fe6963c3565c8a5ceb526.webm?t=1681233034\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/349250/extras/0014c21e2c2fe6963c3565c8a5ceb526.mp4?t=1681233034\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Other stuff:</h2>• <strong>13 worlds</strong> in story mode, with over 20 bosses total<br>• <strong>Hard Mode</strong> as a continuation of the main story, with new enemies and cutscenes<br>• <strong>Endless Mode</strong> with 37 environments, and bosses with randomized attacks<br>• <strong>Play as Savant</strong>, with completely different abilities and 100 new weapons<br>• <strong>A free demo</strong> with 5 worlds, the standard path in Endless, and a limited version of the editor",
